{"tid":1231950,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"各位，下一步到人工島","createTime":"2019-06-16T14:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T15:52:23.000Z","uid":202022,"like":34,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"341ad7908a6d816fec70af53749be87bea47a515","tid":1231950,"uid":202022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好比7婆偷雞"},{"pid":"79984f24907b1b4dcc4a267ef8411bd18009c82c","tid":1231950,"uid":202022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:05:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c39db961bf241526c5c8cbbe8f01fac35a626a3","tid":1231950,"uid":202022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:07:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab2385e5a174c27333e682da9b7390019a7941a5","tid":1231950,"uid":202022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:10:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ac75005c0070ec1a9a6c9af466ddab05af02ddb","tid":1231950,"uid":202022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:12:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4dce93d032b13637c770ffd5a32f14debfc9617","tid":1231950,"uid":124859,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:13:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港國民現要求林鄭午夜前答覆<br />\n- 下台<br />\n- 釋放928/魚蛋/612全數政治囚犯<br />\n- 撤回修例<br />\n- 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n- 即時取消雙程證移民<br />\n- 重啟政改，實現真普選<br />\n<br />\n否則港人應立即宣布 廢除特別行政區政府 成立臨時香港議會 泛民領袖應即是前往美國領使館 要求南海美軍即時介入</span></span>"},{"pid":"b39a2eb71cb9487791a7391afa26f6d7729e039c","tid":1231950,"uid":157938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:13:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n<br />\n繼續做野 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>TVB在反送中報導一事，已經嚴重違反電視通用業務守則中有關「第9章準確、持平及公正」，當中要求「持牌人必須盡一切合理努力，確保新聞、時事節目...的真實資料準確無誤」，以及「持牌人必須確保新聞節目...能夠恰當地持平」，「不可使用謬誤資料或歪曲事實。持牌人亦不應錯誤引導觀眾，以致對節目提及的人士或團體不公平」<br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中的報導完全扭曲事相，報導嚴重偏袒警方和政府，報導失實 ， 偏頗，例如6月12日的「六點半新聞報道」和「晚間新聞」，完全不播放及不提及：<br />\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n6.隻字不提有市民於6月15日於太古廣場因展示示威標語墮樓, 送院搶救後不治的事實<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=q0LkGBAelTJmoxhYCIypyR9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=9df0d00a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">日期： 2019/6/12 時間1830 新聞報導</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"06ba865c75f9e5e10559a6e29d26d60c3d1e18af","tid":1231950,"uid":2106,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:13:32.000Z","msg":"呢件事社會上正反意見都有<br />\n唔會好似今次逃犯條例咁激烈"},{"pid":"d72e13b2840c4586ec5ccca2fb1acdf63572b414","tid":1231950,"uid":202022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06ba865c75f9e5e10559a6e29d26d60c3d1e18af","tid":1231950,"uid":2106,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:13:32.000Z","msg":"呢件事社會上正反意見都有<br />\n唔會好似今次逃犯條例咁激烈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:14:18.000Z","msg":"一睇就知大白象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><